"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1911925-Andy-Murray-Paris-Olympics-doubt\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Murray has revealed he is still not \\\"100% sure\\\" to play in the Olympics despite being named in the GB team on Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.857880145705466e-45, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 106, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9890195141764581, \"rank\": 0.009099132689747096, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The double gold medallist has been handed a wildcard to play in the singles for a record fifth time.\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the Scot, who appeared at Queen's Club in his red GB tracksuit, and Dan Evans have also been nominated as a second British doubles pairing in Paris.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9890195141764581, \"rank\": 0.009099132689747096, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.9814658863853354, \"rank\": 0.01888411354575377, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.953440718850676, \"rank\": 0.028670211485518803, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999992745731918, \"rank\": 7.254273859430777e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ITF will give a decision by June 25.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 384, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITF_World_Tennis_Tour\", \"score\": 0.7287334771231337, \"rank\": 0.37218833013991304, \"text\": \"ITF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITF_World_Tennis_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITF_World_Tennis_Tour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray, 37, will play doubles with Evans at the Cinch Championships this week before playing Wimbledon with his brother Jamie.\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2668141738496985e-27, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999893706964149, \"rank\": 1.0629416480682232e-05, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that could yet be his farewell appearance if he decides against going back to Roland Garros and playing the Olympics.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999980700977609, \"rank\": 7.286479765344047e-07, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if he would play the singles if he is not also in the doubles, Murray said: \\\"I am not 100% sure.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2668141738496985e-27, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It depends a little bit physically how I am doing and a bit how the next few weeks go as well.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But my plan just now is to play but it's not straightforward.\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously I have really enjoyed playing the Olympics over the years and the chance to play in another one, I am excited about that.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously find out in the next 10 days or so on the doubles what's going to happen though but hopefully me and Evo get the chance to play.\\\"\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray is in the squad along with new British No.1 Jack Draper, Cam Norrie and Dan Evans and doubles specialists Joe Salisbury and Neal Skupski.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1208, \"end\": 1214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2668141738496985e-27, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.953440718850676, \"rank\": 0.028670211485518803, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1259, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.9926967693036086, \"rank\": 0.007352941176469691, \"text\": \"Jack Draper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\"}, {\"begin\": 1287, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.9814658863853354, \"rank\": 0.01888411354575377, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  The world No.97, had cast doubt on playing in Paris after losing in the first round in Stuttgart last week.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999992745731918, \"rank\": 7.254273859430777e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Porsche_Tennis_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.9963074421660637, \"rank\": 0.002770415565796407, \"text\": \"Stuttgart\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Porsche_Tennis_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Porsche_Tennis_Grand_Prix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Physically I'd been struggling,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Over the clay season I was struggling a lot with my back and could not really serve properly and preparations were difficult.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I wasn't sure whether or not I was definitely going to play.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had an operation on my back in 2013.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And even before then, clay was the surface that gave me the most problems for my back.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some of it comes from some of the issues I had with my right hip because I lacked movement and rotation in my right hip then my left lower back would have to make up for that.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It would take a bit of the stress and strain.\\\"\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the clay courts, balls generally are bouncing much higher and the issue that I had with my back was extension and rotation.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My back's been pretty good since moving on to the grass.\\\"\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Five-time champion Murray will play his first round match against a qualifier - and would then face the winner of No.7 seed Holger Rune and Aussie Jordan Thompson in the second round if he gets through.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2658, \"end\": 2664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2668141738496985e-27, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2763, \"end\": 2774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holger_Rune\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Holger Rune\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holger_Rune\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holger_Rune\"}, {\"begin\": 2786, \"end\": 2801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Thompson_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.9920171090555051, \"rank\": 0.0037318405970944053, \"text\": \"Jordan Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Thompson_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Thompson_(tennis)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2980, \"end\": 2993, \"title\": \